&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Company Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Fortis Fire &amp;amp; Safety, we provide industry-leading fire protection &amp;amp; security services across the United States. Our ever-growing footprint can be seen in California, Florida, North Carolina, and Chicago, and we are acquiring new brands all the time.&lt;/p&gt;
