&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Integrated Fire &amp;amp; Security Solutions Orlando, FL team is seeking a motivated and relationship driven Account Executive to lead sales and customer development initiatives across the low-voltage systems portfolio. This is a high‑impact, proactive sales role focused on building strong partnerships with end users, general contractors (GCs), electrical contractors (ECs), and select bid‑market opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
