&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CCTV &amp;amp; Video Surveillance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Security Systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access Control Solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Intercom &amp;amp; Sound Systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paging Systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Structured Cabling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fire Alarm Systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recurring Services (Monitoring, Maintenance, Inspections)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Additional emerging technologies as added to the portfolio&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
